<section class="hero">
<div class="hero-text">
<h2>The Story of Salvage</h2>
<p>Step inside the Lane/Heffern House and explore Salvage through fishing heritage, family histories, schooners, textiles, music, craft, and everyday life.</p>

<div class="buttons">
<a class="button" href="#visitor-info">Plan Your Visit</a>
<a class="button secondary" href="exhibits.html">Explore Exhibits</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="visitor-info" class="notice">
<div class="admission-box">
<span>Visit</span>
<strong>By donation</strong>
<small>Card and cash accepted</small>
</div>
<div class="hours-box">
<span>Hours</span>
<p><strong>Tuesday to Saturday</strong> 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Sunday</strong> 12:00 PM - 5:00 PM</p>
</div>
